          "href": "https://support.pagerduty.com/v1/docs/user-roles#section-checking-your-user-role"
        }}>{`Checking Your User Role`}</a>{` or `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://support.pagerduty.com/docs/user-roles#section-changing-user-roles"
