          }}></path></svg></a>{`In PagerDuty`}</h2>
    <p>{`You can integrate Amazon EventBridge from any of your PagerDuty services to your AWS Account(s). This is beneficial for creating an incident-driven workflow with AWS supported integrations and partners.`}</p>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">{`From the `}<strong parentName="li">{`Configuration`}</strong>{` menu, select `}<strong parentName="li">{`Services`}</strong>{`.`}</li>
